ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the product discovery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms and user preferences to recommend new and exciting products tailored to your interests. Simply input your likes and dislikes, and we'll curate a personalized selection of items for you to explore.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Are the products on the app available for purchase?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes! Most products featured in our app are available for purchase. We provide direct links to trusted retailers where you can buy the items that catch your eye. Some products may be concept designs or pre-release items, which will be clearly marked.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: How often are new products added to the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: We update our product database daily to ensure you always have access to the latest and most innovative items. Our team of curators works tirelessly to bring you fresh and exciting products across various categories.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Can I save or bookmark products for later?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Absolutely! Our app allows you to save your favorite discoveries to personalized lists or boards. You can organize products by category, create wish lists, or share your finds with friends and family. Your saved items will be synced across all your devices for easy access.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions? We've got answers to help you discover amazing new products.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the product discovery process work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms and user preferences to recommend new and exciting products tailored to your interests. Simply browse, like, or skip items to refine your recommendations.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Are the products on the app available for purchase?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes! When you find a product you love, you can easily purchase it through our app. We partner with various retailers to ensure a seamless buying experience.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How often are new products added to the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: We update our product catalog daily, ensuring you always have fresh and exciting items to discover. Our team constantly scouts for innovative and trending products across various categories.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I save products for later or create wishlists?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! You can save products to your favorites or create custom wishlists for different occasions. This makes it easy to keep track of items you're interested in or share them with friends and family.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Is there a way to share product discoveries with friends?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, sharing is caring! You can easily share products you love with friends through the app. Simply tap the share button on any product page to send it via text, email, or your favorite social media platform.
